Supreme Court — Appellate Term, March, 1900.

Before Truax, P. J., Scott and Dugro, JJ.

Magdalena Schwartz, Respondent, v. The Supreme Lodge, Knights and Ladies of Honor, Appellant.

Appeal from a judgment in favor of plaintiff. Henry F. Lippold, for Appellant; Roesch & Steiner, for Respondent. Judgment affirmed, with costs. No opinion.
